<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Lan</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset margin and padding */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Full height body and html for flexbox layout */
        html,
        body {
            height: 100%;
            /* Makes sure the page takes up the full height */
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Flexbox layout for body to make footer stick to the bottom */
        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        /* Main content area */
        .container {
            flex: 1;
            /* This makes sure the container takes up the remaining space */
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Header Section */
        header {
            background-color: #861e9b;
            color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* Paragraph spacing */
        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            /* Adds space below each paragraph */
            line-height: 1.6;
            /* Adjusts line height for better readability */
        }
        
        h2#services {
            margin-top: 40px; /* Adds space above "Our Services" */
        }

        /* Footer Styling */
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Navbar Section -->
    <%- include('partials/navbar1.ejs') %>

        <!-- Header Section -->
        <header>
            <h1>Welcome to Lan</h1>
            <p>Your destination for relaxation, wellness, and rejuvenation.</p>
        </header>

        <!-- Main Content Section -->
        <div class="container">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>At Lan, we believe that massage therapy is more than just a luxury; it’s an essential part of your
                self-care
                routine. Our mission is to provide you with a peaceful, healing environment where you can relax, relieve
                stress, and promote your overall well-being.</p>

            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded in 2015, we have been offering high-quality massage therapy services to our community. Whether
                you're seeking relief from chronic pain, looking to unwind after a long day, or simply want to improve
                your physical and mental health, we are here to meet your needs. Our expert therapists are dedicated to
                making
                your experience enjoyable and effective.</p>

            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Professional and Experienced Therapists:</strong> Our therapists are highly trained and
                    certified in various techniques, including Swedish, deep tissue, sports, and therapeutic massage.
                </li>
                <li><strong>Personalized Treatments:</strong> We tailor each session to meet your specific needs,
                    whether it's stress relief, pain management, or relaxation.</li>
                <li><strong>Serene and Relaxing Environment:</strong> Our massage studio is designed to create a calming
                    atmosphere that helps you unwind and experience true relaxation.</li>
                <li><strong>Commitment to Your Well-Being:</strong> We believe in treating the whole person—mind, body,
                    and spirit. Your comfort and health are our top priority.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <p>We offer a variety of massage therapy services designed to help you feel your best. Some of our most
                popular services include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Deep Tissue Massage</li>
                <li>Hot Stone Massage</li>
                <li>Sports Massage</li>
                <li>Therapeutic Massage for Pain Relief</li>
                <li>Custom Treatments Tailored to Your Needs</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer Section -->
        <footer>
            <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>
        </footer>

</body>

</html>